These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, september, april
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, bolivar, alhambra
1. the person who's birthday is in november is the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
3. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Birthday   | november | april | september    |
| Cigar     | bolivar    | alhambra       | montecristo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, peas, corn
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, august, january
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person eating corn is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating peas is the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Food     | corn | pineapple | peas  |
| Birthday   | july  | august  | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, fanta, cola
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, aquamarine, grey
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking fanta is the person who likes grey##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage           | cola | fanta | juice |
| Color   | green        | grey    | aquamarine        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, musicianing, argentine
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, nurse, lawyer
1. the argentine is on the left of the musicianing##1
2. the argentine is on the left or right of the musicianing##3
3. the musician is between the argentine and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Nationality   | argentine | musicianing | australian |
| Job     | nurse  | musician    | lawyer  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
House: tower, wooden, palace
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, reading, singing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the tower house##3
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the tower house##1
4. the tower house is between the wooden house and the person who's hobby is singing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| House   | wooden | tower | palace |
| Hobby     | reading   | skydiving   | singing   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, azalea, lily
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, german, russian
1. the russian is on the left of the spanish##1
2. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Flower   | lily | marigold | azalea      |
| Nationality     | german  | russian | spanish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, mauve, turquise
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, filmmaking, board-games
1. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Color   | mauve  | turquise    | lilac       |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | board-games | gardening |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
House: tower, craftsman, townhouse
3 different pets are kept: fish, snake, rabbit
1. the tower house is the owner of the fish##1
2. the owner of the snake is in the middle##1
3. the townhouse house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
4. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| House   | townhouse        | craftsman  | tower   |
| Pet       | rabbit | snake | fish |

