.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-9::.
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, australian, colombian
City: nizza, rome, hamburg
1. the egyptian is on the left or right of the australian##3
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the colombian##1
3. the australian is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3    |
| Nationality           | egyptian | australian | colombian |
| City   | hamburg    | nizza | rome     |

