.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-10::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, chestnut, lilac
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, june, may
1. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |
| Color      | pink | chestnut    | lilac      |
| Birthday   | june       | november | may |

