.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-11::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, rose, iris
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, bike, taxi
1. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growslily##1
2. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2       |       3        |
| Flower   | iris | rose         | lily          |
| Transport        | jet-ski | bike | taxi |

