.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-12::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, freelancer, electrician
3 different games are played: whist, chess, monopoly
1. the person playing whist is between the doctor and the freelancer##2
2. the person playing chess is the freelancer##1
3. the freelancer is on the left of the electrician##1
4. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the doctor##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Job      | freelancer    | electrician    | doctor  |
| Game   | chess | whist | monopoly |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, december, march
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, collecting, chess
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Birthday   | november | march | december |
| Hobby           | collecting    | chess    | sudoku       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-14::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, scientific, spy
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, motorbike, taxi
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
3. the person driving the taxi is the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy    | western   | scientific |
| Transport   | motorbike | taxi | car |

