2. the person playing poker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Game           | backgammon | mah-jongg | poker |
| Cigar   | prince  | tiparillo    | fonseca     |

