.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-16::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bolivar, aristoff
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, mirinda
1. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking iced-tea##2
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is the prince-smoker##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |
| Cigar   | bolivar | aristoff | prince |
| Beverage   | iced-tea     | milk  | mirinda    |

