The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, family, action
1. the person watching superhero movies is the cain-smoker##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
4. the pall-mall-smoker is the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |    3    |
| Cigar       | old-henry    | pall-mall | cain  |
| Movie-Genre   | family | action        | superhero |

