.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-18::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, hiking, card-games
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, egyptian, russian
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is in the middle##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
4. the malaysian is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |       3       |
| Hobby       | filmmaking | hiking | card-games |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | egyptian   | russian    |

