.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, soy-milk, lemonade
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, bike, roller
1. the person drinking sprite is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
3. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |
| Beverage          | soy-milk | lemonade    | sprite |
| Transport   | roller      | bike | quad-bike  |

