.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, volleyball, snowboarding
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, january, february
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Sport      | snowboarding    | volleyball | basketball         |
| Birthday   | february | january  | march |

 